{"tid":82822,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"識玩揚琴嘅同我入一入嚟","createTime":"2017-01-16T09:08:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-16T13:29:34.000Z","uid":31181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6509153fd655c2e3e500724caa1605e8ceea4113","tid":82822,"uid":31181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T09:08:08.000Z","msg":"我覺得呢樣野好唔抵學<br />\n學術嚟講<br />\n夾樂團又唔係成日做主角<br />\n又冇咩歌專俾呢樣野玩<br />\n<br />\n現實嚟講<br />\n識鋼琴 溝女個時可以 扮唔覺意行過琴鋪 show off 下<br />\n如果用嚟求婚更加唔好講 <br />\nSet 琴又要時間 搬嗰時又驚佢走音<br />\n搞得嚟 條女都走左啦<br />\n<br />\n加上琴線有成百幾條 香港環境潮濕  敲兩敲又斷咗<br />\n養得好辛苦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 五級 中學畢業之後冇再學"},{"pid":"3b5eef7c7f6fbf6a0c2cbcf37e6d04277e0f0d4b","tid":82822,"uid":75870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T11:33:11.000Z","msg":"有個frd打揚琴 問佢要換弦點算<br />\n佢答我話直接買部新<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為要換好耐(好似係)<br />\n<br />\nbut係幾好聽既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f3397858b4a2704caf17e22b01b30ab3b6f0199","tid":82822,"uid":31181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T13:29:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有個frd打揚琴 問佢要換弦點算<br />\n佢答我話直接買部新<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為要換好耐(好似係)<br />\n<br />\nbut係幾好聽既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}